          "character": "firefly",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "text": "How YOU doin', Heena? Welcome to the ultimate 90s Central Cafe! Could this place BE any more cozy?"
        },
        {
          "character": "heena",
          "emotion": "curious",
          "text": "Oh wow, it looks like a sitcom set! I see the big orange sofa, a coffee mug, and... a guitar?"
        },
        {
          "character": "firefly",
          "emotion": "excited",
          "text": "Exactly! But we have a cookie crisis. Find the 5 hidden baking ingredients (Milk, Chocolate, Eggs, Flour, and Sugar) so we can bake birthday cookies!"
        }
      ]
    },
